ndustry \n\t Have worked in interior project especially in Malls or department store \n\t Demonstrated ability to manage multiple projects simultaneously and deliver them on time and within budget \n\t Strong technical knowledge of interior design principles, materials, and construction methods \n\t Excellent communication and stakeholder management skills, with the ability to liaise effectively with clients, contractors, and the design team \n\t Proficient in using project management software and tools, such as AutoCAD, SketchUp, and Microsoft Project \n\t A degree in interior design, architecture, or a related field is preferred \n\t Lives in Jakarta Greater Area \n\t Able to work on weekends and/or public holidays  \n\t Fluent in English \n\t Have worked on mall retail stores fitout is preferred \n\t Understands well on MEP"}
