m operations (VM, host, cluster, datastore management, and basic performance troubleshooting). \n\t \n\t \n\t Experience in HCI environment monitoring, cluster/node operations, and basic issue handling. \n\t \n\t \n\t Experience managing enterprise-grade servers and storage systems. \n\t \n\t \n\t Strong understanding of monitoring, incident handling, SLA compliance, and infrastructure documentation practices."}
